\[
q_{\text{sys}}=\Delta H_{\text{vap}}=+29.4\;\text{kJ mol}^{-1}=+2.94\times10^{4}\;\text{J mol}^{-1}
\]

The temperature at which the phase change occurs is the normal boiling temperature:

\[
T = 334.88\;\text{K}
\]

Hence

\[
